{"tid":1666910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食住個勢] 民陣好應該趁今次機會搞一次南亞與穆斯林we connect大遊行","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:46:13.000Z","uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0df60f64ccd7d4a4af6b1ca01f72d22d2e62012","tid":1666910,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"警隊高層、特首陸續拜訪清真寺，可見佢地其實堅係怕得罪伊斯蘭世界<br />\n所以民陣好應該趁今次機會申請今個星期日嚟一次香港人we connect南亞族裔與伊斯蘭教徒既和平遊行<br />\n如果佢批不反對通知書，就可以嚟多一次200萬+1既遊行。<br />\n如果佢唔批不反對通知書，就可以話佢打壓小數族裔同宗教既權利。"},{"pid":"9ac69a1d02da2a079e0ab4c91a0c7e0ab92045f9","tid":1666910,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d67bf6304bc5f33e66e20f6d4838ad44696b42","tid":1666910,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"諗得過<br />\n但要拎到南亞同穆斯林既同意先<br />\n唔係會俾人話利用唔尊重"},{"pid":"776fca23bc47bd1f1d01eb9ef114a5e534c940e9","tid":1666910,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"1af64fabab168405e6c712521d9545fdb919802a","tid":1666910,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d67bf6304bc5f33e66e20f6d4838ad44696b42","tid":1666910,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"諗得過<br />\n但要拎到南亞同穆斯林既同意先<br />\n唔係會俾人話利用唔尊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"重點"}]}